# CLion CMake Presets
# This file helps CLion configure the project with optimal settings

# Recommended CLion Settings:
# - Build Directory: cmake-build-debug (for Debug) or cmake-build-release (for Release)
# - CMake options: -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug (or Release)
# - Build target: ValveExplorer
# - Run target: ValveExplorer

